<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title><%= locals.subjectLine || 'Password Reset Request' %></title>
    <style>
        :root {
            --lavender-lightest-yellow: #FDFBD4;
            --lavender-muted-green: #BDB96A;
            --lavender-light-blue: #C1BFFF;
            --lavender-very-light: #DBD4FF;
            --lavender-vibrant-purple: #CF6DFC;
            --lavender-darker-purple: #a358d3;
        }
        body { font-family: 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #343a40; margin: 0; padding: 0; background-color: var(--lavender-very-light); }
        .email-wrapper { width: 100%; background-color: var(--lavender-very-light); padding: 20px 0; }
        .container { width: 100%; max-width: 600px; margin: 20px auto; background-color: #ffffff; border-radius: 12px; box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.1); overflow: hidden; border: 1px solid var(--lavender-light-blue); }
        .header { background-color: var(--lavender-light-blue); padding: 30px 20px; text-align: center; }
        .logo { max-height: 60px; width: auto; display: block; margin: 0 auto 15px; }
        .header h1 { margin: 10px 0 0 0; font-size: 22px; font-weight: 600; color: #343a40; }
        .content { padding: 30px; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.7; }
        .content p { margin-bottom: 18px; }
        .otp-card { margin: 25px 0; padding: 20px; background-color: var(--lavender-lightest-yellow); border-radius: 8px; text-align: center; border: 1px dashed var(--lavender-muted-green); }
        .otp-card .otp-title { margin-bottom: 10px; color: var(--lavender-darker-purple); font-weight: 500;}
        .otp-code { font-size: 32px; font-weight: 700; color: var(--lavender-vibrant-purple); letter-spacing: 4px; display: inline-block; padding: 8px 15px; background-color: #fff; border-radius: 6px; border: 1px solid var(--lavender-very-light); }
        .button-container { text-align: center; margin: 25px 0; }
        .button { display: inline-block; padding: 12px 28px; background-color: var(--lavender-vibrant-purple); color: #ffffff !important; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 8px; font-weight: 600; font-size: 16px; box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.1); }
        .button:hover { background-color: var(--lavender-darker-purple); }
        .link-alt { color: var(--lavender-darker-purple); text-decoration: none; }
        .link-alt:hover { text-decoration: underline; }
        .footer { text-align: center; padding: 25px; font-size: 13px; color: #6c757d; background-color: var(--lavender-lightest-yellow); border-top: 1px solid var(--lavender-light-blue); }
        .footer p { margin: 5px 0; }
        .footer a { color: var(--lavender-darker-purple); text-decoration: none; }
         @media screen and (max-width: 600px) { .otp-code { font-size: 24px; letter-spacing: 3px;} }
    </style>
</head>
<body style="margin:0; padding:0; background-color: var(--lavender-very-light);">
    <table class="email-wrapper" border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="100%">
        <tr><td align="center" valign="top">
        <table class="container" border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="600" style="border-collapse: collapse;">
            <tr><td class="header">
                <% if (typeof logoUrl !== 'undefined' && logoUrl) { %>
                    <img src="<%= logoUrl %>" alt="<%= process.env.EMAIL_FROM_NAME || 'Site Logo' %>" class="logo">
                <% } %>
                <h1>Password Reset Request</h1>
            </td></tr>
            <tr><td class="content">
                <p>Hello <%= customerName %>,</p>
                <p>We received a request to reset your password for your Mynet Customer Portal account. If you did not make this request, you can ignore this email.</p>

                <div class="otp-card">
                    <p class="otp-title">Your One-Time Password (OTP) is:</p>
                    <div class="otp-code"><%= otp %></div>
                </div>

                <p style="text-align: center;">Alternatively, you can click the button below to reset your password directly:</p>
                <div class="button-container">
                    <a href="<%= resetLink %>" class="button">Reset Your Password</a>
                </div>

                <p>This OTP and reset link are valid for <strong>10 minutes</strong>.</p>
                <p>If you are having trouble clicking the button, copy and paste this URL into your web browser:<br> <a href="<%= resetLink %>" class="link-alt"><%= resetLink %></a></p>

                <p>Thank you,<br>The <%= process.env.EMAIL_FROM_NAME || 'Mynet Team' %></p>
            </td></tr>
            <tr><td class="footer">
                <p>&copy; <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> <%= process.env.EMAIL_FROM_NAME || 'Mynet' %>. All rights reserved.</p>
                <% if (locals.siteUrl) { %><p><a href="<%= siteUrl %>" class="link-alt">Visit our website</a></p><% } %>
                <p>
                    Need help? Contact us at <a href="mailto:<%= process.env.CONTACT_RECEIVER_EMAIL %>" class="link-alt"><%= process.env.CONTACT_RECEIVER_EMAIL %></a>
                    <% if (process.env.COMPANY_PHONE) { %> | Phone: <%= process.env.COMPANY_PHONE %><% } %>
                </p>
            </td></tr>
        </table>
        </td></tr>
    </table>
</body>
</html>
